item.title: Under-graduate
item.description: Soon after a hectic year of study and exams, began a year with power-packed experiences. I could recall a fortuitous incidence. A year ago I, while returning to my home, from the Venugopal temple, lost my way and ended up in the crowded Manipal Campus. At that moment I saw myself to be a student there in the distant hypothetical future. Destiny aligned with my interests, received admission there, in my favorite branch.
